snippet.textDisplay: Petition for @cokestudioindia to compose a song with himachali roots  as many people miss out the true joy of himachali songs .our himachal is much more than hill station it has its folklore that confides its golden history wrapped in its songs there is much more than rodhu jana meri ammiye and chamba kitni k door and I personally think that after the successfulness of sonchadi u people can provide our folklore a worldwide stage too....just one recommendation that if this comment reaches up to u could u do something with folklore of chamba as it is amuch lesser known area but is heavenly beautiful the ravi river the kailash kinnar range the abode of lord Shiva it has various stories of kings and queens how the ravi came to chamba the sacrifices of our queen theres a lot hope u will do something about this petition ❤
